{"tid":536802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門統計局　15年普通話人數增3倍　廣東話人數激跌一成","createTime":"2018-01-22T06:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T11:56:05.000Z","uid":47714,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0eb6a1233ca749bc0a795e04fb27fbe63e07e9d3","tid":536802,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:44:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/abbotmacau/photos/a.288535868156292.1073741828.254213211588558/584145971928612/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fabbotmacau%2Fphotos%2Fa.288535868156292.1073741828.254213211588558%2F584145971928612%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=6o%2FaKrh4JSVLpiNygGOh3kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=defafdd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/abbotmacau/photos/a.288535868156292.1073741828.254213211588558/584145971928612/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n&lt;&lt;廣東話地位問題真係受到好大挑戰&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n之前開帖講廣話的後生仔比例跌左！<br />\n沃門通街都係普通話，<br />\n連法定的葡文比菲律賓話低！？<br />\n大中小學開始唔講廣東話<br />\n<br />\n澳門街的家長仲夠膽話唔擔心!?<br />\n嘩原來而家學校用普通話教學，<br />\n唔通等到仔女都唔肯同講粵語！<br />\n你先識驚?！<br />\n<br />\n其實講普通話的人係多左3倍多！<br />\n想知點解廣東話的地位受到動搖！？<br />\n大家要留意今晚十時的方丈講場！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/QDaesj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FQDaesj&h=e1c86c2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a45599a1209aae5394d1f2fa28aa43dbd8802a8","tid":536802,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c467ae52ef84037c6aa6a46d71d9176533b3b3c3","tid":536802,"uid":3748,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:57:28.000Z","msg":"乜澳門母語唔係普通話咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075b2259109721ab6d1b86e6ec875f23b9ac101a","tid":536802,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:01:39.000Z","msg":"香港差唔多"},{"pid":"f451c92fdb4b0aea